Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why I can't play well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:34.84,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,78.666667)}The Rainy Season Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:34.84,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,434)}The Glass Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Identification?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tissues?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Map?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sidearm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grenades?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's joking, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that? You scared me there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had calmly thought about it, you would've realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was mean, Rio-senpai.{I think we used "senpai" instead of "sempai" the entire time}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like their relationship has been improving lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio's almost like an overly fretful mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. This is today's list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mission today is to head into town to buy the supplies on that list, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then. Drive safely now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceeding with departure.{Same thing she said in episode 3, verified and copied from there.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come home soon!{Normally, I'd use "come back soon!", but since it's Filicia, this fits her better}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having pot-au-feu tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.78,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a mother, eh?{while}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time isn't it, Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the two of us to come into town together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this is basically my first time going into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally different from during the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very peaceful and quiet town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first one was a Nue, a roof ornament that is found only in Trois.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is used to ward off evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next one was a drinking fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its carved head was modeled after the twelfth Helvetian Archduke, Akira Arkadia II.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things from before... {durf}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders were to drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan, you sure are smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coming in or not? Could you hurry up and decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blocking the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the old lady from the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Young{\i0} lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Splitting hairs. Bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an intractable child as always, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about calling me Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the next shipment is next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, does she know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, you girls are such an unusual bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're soldiers—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were interested in that when you first arrived, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... C-Can I touch it?{SEXUAL INNUENDO #1}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fish, right? What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dolphin, which was closer to a human than a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a marine mammal that lived when there was still life in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean? They lived in the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old guy is quite good at making this type of stuff, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, his face doesn't look it, but he's quite the romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the one who made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a large workshop on the outskirts of town. All of this glasswork comes from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it — the place where they're made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are heading there next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So Takemikazuchi's parts are also made there, huh?{Correct Takemicaduchi? How're we doing this now?! lol}{Screw it. If the Japanese can't be consistent, then we'll just stick with this >_>}{fair enough}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. Naomi is also collecting parts from the previous age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Noël-chan, you sure are amazing! You can fix that complex machine in a jiffy.{I hope "jiffy" isn't too localized}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a jiffy? {Onomatopoeia, but you can figure out how to make it work}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even memorize all of the bugle's signal codes. My head's at its limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:08:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is really... not that difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Machines... will not... betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your change is 2,750,000 yen! {inflation much?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! We get that much back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incorrect. Our change should be 2.75 yen. {oh... this guy should be bankrupt by now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as always, Noël-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your change. {1 yen piece is round and bronzish, 10 sen piece is a squared-off rectangle, 5 sen is rounded corners of the same.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that's been playing the bugle in the morning recently is you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not that good. Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay; I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it... It completely wakes me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that I need to hurry up and master it, so I don't cause trouble for the people of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I...{while}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.98,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! You ran into someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It's you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the clueless girl. {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.69,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you fully recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-san, they have nothing to do with your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all the same! I hate soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the heck out of town!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day, you play that bugle horridly in the morning! {maybe change to "Day after day, in the morning, you..." as it matches his speech a bit better with the repetition}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really very sorry for his rudeness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a war orphan, so when he sees a soldier he becomes really angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are soldiers, and that is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right... We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I enlisted, I also swore the Oath of Paradores.{Sounds correct, mebbe get teh frenchloli to check?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I had believed I understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew what was involved from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to be unsure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The more time I spend, the better I'll become.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there isn't a signal bugle, everyone will be troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the glass factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Noël-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've seen such a large building!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's no good either?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a problem with the aberration?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The refraction shouldn't be the issue... {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm the new recruit, Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, uh... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it until the error came up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seek time was virtually the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The distortion around the peripheral was smaller than before.{while}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:32.64,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss doesn't see anything else when he starts working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's amazing, that Carl-ojisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He holds the title of Meister that only five people in the nation have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He once won a competition in the capital and even presented his work to the Archduke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, if you have time to chit chat, why don't you go work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Sorry, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Meister title is a stupid little thing anyway.{TLC-sounds fine, but could prolly use some 'gruffing'}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good enough to make this right yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Takemikazuchi optical sensor lens. {tank name again}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the original one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to repair Takemikazuchi, we require two more of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I requested to have them made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is not going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're this pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the lenses, there is more to them than just silicon dioxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also mixed in are sodium oxide and magnesium oxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, there are chromatic and peripheral aberrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it corrects the distortion of images.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we do not know the distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing is like some ancient, magic item.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that glass was just pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite difficult, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can collect high quality silicon in Seize,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there are several small factories that primarily work on hand-made art.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This factory is one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when the war intensified,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the need for glass increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, this factory became larger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I like machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But machines can also hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemikazuchi must have also killed many people in the past. {robo-name again}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, machines for killing people... really are terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, maybe the scary part isn't the machine itself, but rather the people who used it, right?{DID SHE SAY SOMETHING THAT MAKES LOGICAL SENSE FOR ONCE?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, take a look at this bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like that when I play it, but when Rio-senpai plays it, it sings beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanks must be the same way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And recently, Rio-senpai played the song from inside Takemikazuchi for me.{Tank namey}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sang so beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was a good tank — the Takemikazuchi.{again}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, next time let's—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her sleep for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She usually doesn't sleep at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan works real hard... to fix up the Takemikazuchi.{you know it}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This young lady is a real craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else I wouldn't have taken such a troublesome request.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Cover her with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you girls dropped by Windmill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Naomi-san doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Naomi-san also said that he was a wonderful romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that? Isn't that great, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Hurry up and get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He's angry. Time to get back to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is that old technology really that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But the boss always says:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No matter how amazing it is, as long as humans made it, there's no way we can't do it either!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... or so I'd like to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Rio-san's playing is very different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so envious. I don't know if I'll be able to play it like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to work as hard as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my lips — here, look — they've become this swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how much I play and I play, it still doesn't come out the same as senpai's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have the talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missy.{I like this}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Talent" is the lamest excuse for those who quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about playing bugles...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But young people often find failure here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missy, are you forcing the sound out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to make it into this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The glass, you see, wanted to become like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Carl-ojisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the sound resound the way it wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the sun came out a bit early just for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is also a craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glass will produce different sounds based on the type and amount of impurities it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, even if our ears cannot differentiate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone who has perfect pitch should be able to discern it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata can find the one that sounds closest to the original from all the ones made so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she does, then perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, listen to their voices, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan's changed a lot since she came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked! It worked, Noël-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen Noël smile.
